import React from "react";

ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById("root")).render(
    <StrictMode>
      <GoogleOAuthProvider clientId="787324533252-db3ks4evh8thaordvu8j38votfflsk6p.apps.googleusercontent.com">
        <QueryClientProvider client={queryClient}>
          <ThemeWrapper>
            <TooltipProvider delayDuration={0}>
              <App />
            </TooltipProvider>
            <Toaster position="top-right" reverseOrder={false} />
            {/* <UiToaster /> */}
          </ThemeWrapper>
        </QueryClientProvider>
      </GoogleOAuthProvider>
    </StrictMode>
  );
